div.div: An initial Deptford occupation is indicated by mound & midden excavation; however, its defined area is uncertain as it is masked by the later primary Weeden Island occupation of mound reuse, midden material, etc.

arch:property.oc:show_val: A major Early Weeden Island occupation covers the entire site. Distribution of midden and artifacts indicates a horseshoe-shaped occupation area studded by mounds. A mostly ephemeral Deptford component exists but its true extent is currently unknown.
